            "title": "台股低收513點或1.62%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台股顯著下調，台灣加權指數收報31246點，跌513點或1.62%。</p>\n</div>",
