            "title": "半日收市︱反覆略回 恒指再跌39點報26447點 百度再創52周新高成藍籌最強",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股步入五連跌，今早中段倒升後掉頭轉跌，但波幅有限。重磅股亦互有升跌，已連升兩日的百度(09888)再創52周新高，登藍籌升幅榜首。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230712-124437_source-web_09888-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230712-124437_source-web_09888-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：百度官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早跟隨外圍向下，低開90點、見26397點便喘穩，其後跌幅收窄並倒升，進入好淡爭持階段，最高報26567點，升79點，中後段則重新「潛水」，但跌幅維持在百點以內；恒指中午收報26447點，跌39點或0.15%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230712-124437_source-web_09888-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230712-124437_source-web_09888-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：百度官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230712-124447_source-web_百度集團09888-5_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230712-124447_source-web_百度集團09888-5_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：百度官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250624_FI_source-web_603986-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250624_FI_source-web_603986-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：兆易創新官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230712-124437_source-web_09888-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：百度官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230712-124447_source-web_百度集團09888-5_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：百度官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250624_FI_source-web_603986-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：兆易創新官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數亦重新跑贏，早市大部份時間報升，中午收報5691點，升8點或0.15%；國企指數則跌24點或0.26%，報9070點。主板半日成交1276.53億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升1點，報26463點，高水15點。科指期貨升27點，報5701點，高水9點。國指期貨跌11點，報9077點，高水6點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今早的藍籌最強百度，獲多家券商爭相唱好，早市幾乎全程報升，最高見154.4元，漲3.76%；中午收報153.7元，仍漲3.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">券商指出，百度應在農曆年後派發季度成績表，其中摩根士丹利估計，百度上季non-GAAP經營利潤跌40.5%，但核心經營利潤按季改善，今年利潤更可進一步提升，雖然僅維持對該股「平配」建設，但亦將百度在美國市場的股份目標升至150美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美銀同樣相信百度上季核心業務重新按季改善，並看好AI雲市場需求維持強勁，重申對該股「買入」評級，目標價176元。花旗亦維持對百度「買入」評級，考慮該公司分拆崑崙芯上市後估值有望提升，將百度在美國市場股份目標價升至183美元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230712-124447_source-web_百度集團09888-5_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230712-124447_source-web_百度集團09888-5_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：百度官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片與半導體相關股也回復動力，中芯(00981)最高曾升4.3%，高見77.7元；中午收報76.85元，仍漲3.15%，是表現次佳藍籌，半日成交40.24億元。華虹半導體(01347)升4.67%，報105.3元，維持「紅底股」地位，交投4.67億元。兩隻股份均躋身主板股份成交額10大榜上。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">ASMPT(00522)評估SMT解決方案分部策略方案，包括將之出售或分拆；該股今早輕微高開0.87%後持續向好，重新加入「紅底股」行列，半日升4%，報101.5元，創3個月高位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Fabless芯片供應商兆易創新(03986)也A、H齊揚，H股飆11.96%，報342.6元，破頂創新高；兆易創新A股(603986.SH)也升4.37%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250624_FI_source-web_603986-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250624_FI_source-web_603986-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：兆易創新官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「ATMXJ」則互有升跌，當中以阿里巴巴(09988)表現最佳，半日升1.06%，報161.4元。內地媒體引用全球最大AI開源社區Hugging Face最新數據，指阿里通義千問衍生模型數突破20萬個，成為全球首個達成此目標的開源大模型，通義千問系列模型下載量突破10億次，平均每天被下載110萬次，已完全超越美國Llama，穩居開源大模型全球首位。有關報道或是阿里巴巴股份今早動力提升的助力。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於「ATMXJ」餘下4位成員，則只有京東(09618)逆市微升0.27%，報112.7元。騰訊(00700)微跌0.17%，報600元；美團(03690)跌0.77%，報96.6元；小米(01810)弱勢未改，今早創6個月新低，中午收報34.66元，挫2.31%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">運動用品股受壓，安踏(02020)昨收市後公布，安踏品牌產品上季零售額錄低單位數跌幅；該股今早全程報跌，半日挫5.75%，報77.8元，在藍籌中表現包尾。李寧(02331)則是藍籌尾二，半日跌4%，報20.62元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15599398-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e7%95%a5%e5%9b%9e-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%86%8d%e8%b7%8c39%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126447%e9%bb%9e-%e7%99%be%e5%ba%a6%e5%86%8d%e5%89%b552%e5%91%a8",
